{
  "title": "Intense Peppery Dutch Peas Hash",
  "description": "A traditional Dutch dish featuring peas and a mother sauce base, served in a molcajete, this recipe is perfect for meal prep and packs a peppery punch. It is a snappy and flavorful meal that can be prepared in under an hour.",
